output_list.impact: Integer overflow in mintToken function allows unauthorized minting of tokens.
freezeAccount function allows unauthorized users to freeze an arbitrary user's account.
Integer overflow in setPrices function allows unauthorized users to change the sell and buy prices.
Integer overflow in buy function prevents users from buying tokens without specifying the amount.
Integer overflow in sell function allows unauthorized users to set the price of the tokens they will sell.
freeze function allows unauthorized users to freeze an arbitrary user's account.
setOwner function allows unauthorized users to change the owner of the contract.
MorphToken function relies on the owner's address, allowing unauthorized users to change the owner of the contract.
setBalance function allows unauthorized users to set the minimum balance for the tokens.
